{"tid":2152446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基本法一國兩制真相　鄧小平冇可能唔知","createTime":"2020-08-12T03:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T04:43:03.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0c8c9e91ab9c63ced92da102b77ec107c61ec2","tid":2152446,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201911200342.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201911200342.aspx&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfwb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=e3eee681\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201911200342.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n在中共解放軍幾萬人向西藏推進的壓力下，西藏5人代表團1951年在北京簽署和平解放西藏17條協定，也就是中共建政後首次實施的「一國兩制」，中共承諾尊重西藏現行制度與達賴喇嘛、班禪的固有地位與職權、各級官員照常供職，實施宗教信仰自由。<br />\n<br />\n但最終，如同香港「一國兩制」現在面臨的狀況一樣，中共撕毀了協定，強制在西藏推行人民公社、大躍進等政策，摧毀寺院，終於在1959年引爆藏人反共抗暴，與共軍武裝衝突，並導致達賴喇嘛在生命威脅下流亡印度。"},{"pid":"9168d1c3c1d0dbadbb53c880e9ffaabbc7a4a0b4","tid":2152446,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:01:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bdb4694143fbfabba86a8fe451316017a098c2a","tid":2152446,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:04:23.000Z","msg":"個標題應該係：<br />\n基本法一國兩制真相    司徒華、李柱銘冇可能唔知"},{"pid":"554ffc796b7ec521b5a6b029abdd1eeab67aaa66","tid":2152446,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"319ac0d37572f3253d42f645dda969f6047d4a72","tid":2152446,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"梗係係支那人冇國際視野，佢地低估左香港係國際間既地位。<br />\n基本法腐乳講到自己都信埋一份"},{"pid":"c9928735a50e92daab0bfca6e679ad4c09414f64","tid":2152446,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:37:47.000Z","msg":"唔通鄧小平會係香港人咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeaaf063ae72d774ef583c84d5ca2cf267f6